cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper proposes a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) based algorithm for object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The algorithm uses convolutional features trained for segmentation of objects and 'stuff', which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions experiments and performance improvements, which could fall under neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
